              <li>You did not click "Okay" when the Facebook dialog requested permission for Project Borrow</li>
              <li>You unchecked the permission for Project Borrow to access your friend data</li>
            </ol>

            <p>Project Borrow is a sharing site between friends, so we depend on access to your Facebook friends. If you have concerns about how this information will be used, please consult our <%= link_to 'privacy policy', policy_path, { style: "color:#428bca", target: "_blank" } %>. If you would like to go through Facebook authorization again click below. If you've correctly authorized and are still seeing this message, we apologize, please <%= mail_to 'james@projectborrow.com', 'send us an email', { style: "color:#428bca"}%>.</p> 
