          <h4 class="modal-title logo-color" style="margin-bottom: 1%">Get ready to borrow!</h4>
          <p>We'll get you an invitation as soon as we're ready! Until then, we'd love it if you could help spread the word in San Francisco so we can launch sooner.</p>

          <p><b>Do you have friends who have stuff you'd like to borrow? A big tent? An air mattress? Some other gadgets or equipment? This is your chance!</b> Enter your friends' emails below (separate with commas) and we'll send them an anonymous request to join so that if they do, you'll be able to borrow their stuff!</p>

          <div class="col-xs-12">
            <%= form_tag(new_invitee_path, :autocomplete => "off", :id => "referral_form") do -%>
              <%= hidden_field_tag :referer, Rails.env == "test" ? 123 : flash[:new_signup_fb_id] %>
              <%= text_area_tag :emails, nil, class: "form-control", id: "friend_emails", placeholder: "Enter your friend's emails separated by commas" %>
              <%= submit_tag "Send to my friends!", class: "btn btn-primary btn-large btn-block", id: "refer" %>
            <% end -%>
            <p class="horiz" style="font-size:75%; font-style:italic">We send one email per person, and nothing else. For more info, check out our <%= link_to 'privacy policy', policy_path, { style:"color:#428bca", target: "_blank" } %>.</p>
          <hr>
          </div>

          <p class="horiz" style="font-weight:bold">You can also share more broadly by clicking a social media button below!</p>
          <div class="addthis_sharing_toolbox horiz"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer" style="padding:0; margin:0">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

